<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:30:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>德国为中国企业提供更多投资担保</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</link><description>德国经济部的数据显示，德国政府对华投资的国家担保价值在经历大幅下降后，今年有所上升。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/germany-issues-more-investment-guarantees-business-china-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>教宗每周接见活动将于12月起翻译成中文</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</link><description>教皇方济各周三表示，从下周开始，他在梵蒂冈每周公开接见时的教义也将被翻译成中文。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/popes-weekly-audiences-be-translated-into-mandarin-december-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国假期将焦点转向通胀，法国局势紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:18:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在曼哈顿唯一的选举胜利是在下东区的这个街区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普在曼哈顿的每个选区都输给了卡马拉·哈里斯——除了一个选区。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trumps-only-manhattan-electoral-win-is-this-block-lower-east-side-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>小马智行 2.6 亿美元 IPO 衡量美国投资者对中国企业的兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国的小马智行周三表示，已在美国首次公开募股中筹集了 2.6 亿美元，这家机器人出租车初创公司的估值约为 45.5 亿美元，这是寄望于美国市场投资者情绪改善的最新进展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 10:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-robotaxi-startup-pony-ai-raises-260-mln-us-ipo-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行在针对欧盟卡特尔 3340 万美元罚款的法庭诉讼中败诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-court-challenge-against-334-mln-eu-cartel-fine-2024-11-27/</link><description>周三，汇丰银行在针对欧盟卡特尔罚款 3170 万欧元（合 3340 万美元）的诉讼中败诉，此前欧洲第二最高法院在这起旷日持久的案件中支持欧盟监管机构。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 08:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-loses-court-challenge-against-334-mln-eu-cartel-fine-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，10月份国外智能手机在华销量同比下降44.25%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</link><description>一家政府下属的研究公司周三发布的数据显示，10月份包括苹果公司iPhone在内的外国品牌智能手机在中国的销量同比下降了44.25%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foreign-smartphone-sales-china-drop-4425-oct-data-shows-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称国防部长董军接受调查的报道是“追影子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国外交部周三在回应有关中国国防部长董军因腐败接受调查的报道的问题时表示，这“只是追影子”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:27:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-calls-report-that-defence-minister-dong-jun-is-under-probe-shadow-chasing-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>承受多年压力后大众确认计划退出新疆业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-exit-xinjiang-operation-with-sales-local-plant-test-track-sources-say-2024-11-27/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，该公司将出售其在中国新疆的所有业务，多年来，该公司一直面临着越来越大的压力，要求其放弃在该地区的业务，该地区的人权组织记录了针对维吾尔族人口的虐待行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 07:15:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vw-exit-xinjiang-operation-with-sales-local-plant-test-track-sources-say-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国禾赛明年将激光雷达价格减半，预计将在电动汽车中广泛采用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球最大的自动驾驶激光雷达传感器制造商中国禾赛集团表示，计划明年将其主要产品的价格削减一半，这将导致该技术在电动汽车中得到更广泛的采用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 06:02:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-hesai-halve-lidar-prices-next-year-sees-wide-adoption-electric-cars-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝评论被监禁官员薄熙来之子的婚姻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国周三拒绝就被监禁的前领导人薄熙来的儿子与台湾人的婚姻发表评论，只是表示反对对此事的“恶意”猜测。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 04:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-declines-comment-marriage-son-jailed-official-bo-xilai-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国汽车战争加剧，比亚迪要求供应商降价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-sets-negotiable-price-reduction-targets-suppliers-2024-11-27/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪要求其供应商降价，这表明全球最大汽车市场的残酷价格战即将升级。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 04:29:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-sets-negotiable-price-reduction-targets-suppliers-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>股市暂停，货币因特朗普关税担忧而涨跌互现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</link><description>全球股市周三暂停，货币涨跌互现，因投资者担心候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的下一个潜在关税目标，一天前他承诺对加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收新关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国可能因总统太平洋访问而在台湾附近举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</link><description>根据台湾和地区安全官员的评估，中国可能会在未来几天在台湾附近发动军事演习，以总统赖清德即将前往太平洋和计划过境美国为借口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-could-launch-military-drills-near-taiwan-over-presidents-pacific-visit-2024-11-27/</guid></item><item><title>富士康称其全球业务将使其免受特朗普关税的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</link><description>台湾富士康表示，预计特朗普新关税对公司的影响将小于其竞争对手。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 03:17:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwans-foxconn-says-global-manufacturing-footprint-shield-it-trumps-tariffs-2024-11-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>